import {
    Page,
    Navbar,
    Link,
    Panel,
    Block
} from 'framework7-react';

const DetailPage = (props) => {
    return (
        <Page 
            name="list"
        >
            <Navbar title={`Detail of ${props.title}`}>
                <Link slot="left" iconF7="arrowshape_turn_up_left_fill" href="/"></Link>
                <Link slot="right" iconF7="menu" panelOpen="#panel-menu"></Link>
            </Navbar>
            <Panel right cover backdrop closeByBackdropClick containerEl="#list" id="panel-menu">
                <Page>
                    <Block strong>
                        <Link panelClose>My Pokemon List</Link>
                    </Block>
                </Page>
            </Panel>
        </Page>
    )
}

export default DetailPage;
